Let's be nicer to each other 
We're all trying our best ♡

Is friendship  a small thing to you?
Can't you just come nd sit with me?
Can't you just hold me for a sec?
Can't you just listen to me for a moment?
Can't you just feel me for a time?
Can't you just be with me?
CAN'T YOU JUST STAY WITH ME?

I know staying with me isn't easy but I thought you were different but you were not , may be you were but not this time for me...
Today I felt in how many pieces i was, when you left as like everyone .... I felt I was okay but I wasn't because it hurted ...
